{"tid":2221398,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為求生再出招 大推AppGallery進軍遊戲業","createTime":"2020-09-28T10:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T10:20:20.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c27bed19814474f91bbc7fa520f088addbddac","tid":2221398,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"華為遭到美國制裁，被限制近用Google及其App商店Google Play後，仍企圖在App領域中尋求求生機會，在今年度的東京電玩展中，就不斷尋求與遊戲引擎商的合作機會，推動華為自家的App商店AppGallery的營收。<br />\n<br />\n據《日經新聞》報導，這是華為第2次在國際展覽會中推行AppGallery，這次主打的是遊戲，例如華為表示，AppGallery已經與遊戲引擎商Unity建立合作關係等。<br />\n<br />\n華為聲稱，目前AppGallery已可在170多個國家使用，擁有180萬名註冊開發商，但是App總數只有10萬個，遠低於Google Play的300萬個，而且許多極為常用的App都付之闕如。<br />\n<br />\n但是報導指出，這不代表華為這波宣傳的策略是錯誤的，因為雖然Google Play跟蘋果（Apple）的iOS上都有上百萬個App，但是70%的收入來自遊戲，僅今年上半年就貢獻2大App商城共366億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3305120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3305120&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIR5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=eea77f89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3305120&h=6489f5c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3305120</a><br />\n<br />\n日經：<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Huawei-crackdown/Huawei-pitches-Google-Play-rival-to-game-developers-at-Tokyo-expo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FSpotlight%2FHuawei-crackdown%2FHuawei-pitches-Google-Play-rival-to-game-developers-at-Tokyo-expo&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIR5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=33f89fba\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Huawei-crackdown/Huawei-pitches-Google-Play-rival-to-game-developers-at-Tokyo-expo</a>"},{"pid":"039ad083d72e9659a16436482c305b1ad0d1a3ca","tid":2221398,"uid":180851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"又話自煮？去左邊"},{"pid":"4567e7f043a457bcd327d907cf84a2c43b26dcc